	 </p><p><i>Figure 6: Structure of carbon nanotubes: single wall (left) and multi-walled nanotube (right). Copyright Alain Rochefort Assistant Professor Engineering Physics Department, Nanostructure Group, Center for Research on Computation and its Applications (CERCA) </i>(21) <i>.</i> </p><p>
 
